<h3>一. 总则</h3>
<h3>Overall Statement</h3>
<div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>
导师秉承“以学生前途为己任”的理念，对学生文书的修改认真负责，为实现学生成功申请世界名校而共同努力。
</p>
<p>
The Consultant identifies themselves with the morale of “replicating their successes in the students they are serving”. The consultant is to be diligent and maximizing the student’s potential in their application process, in order to achieve offer from the student’s dream university.
</p>
</div>
