<h3>二. 服务说明</h3>
<h3>Services Description</h3>
<div></div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>
导师的基本服务为修改润色（proof reading，refining）学生个人陈述。如果不能进行修改需提供professional comments and feedbacks。
</p>
<p>
The consultant provides the standard services based on proof-reading and refining the student applicant’s personal statement. If this is not available, the baseline is to provide thoroughly professional comments and feedbacks on the original document.
</p>
</div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>
导师的拓展服务为向学生提供Tutorial，话题包括How to make a presentation, Academic Writing, How to avoid plagiarism, How to prepare for examination 等， 具体细节请与UFOffer工作人员协商。
</p>
</div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>
导师的拓展服务还包括向学生提供留学期间的essay修改润色服务，具体细节请与UFOffer工作人员协商。
</p>
<p>
The consultant may also provide premium services including but not limited to the items on:
</p>
<ol>
<li>How to make a course/project presentation</li>
<li>Assistance on academic coursework writing (e.g. “how to avoid plagiarism”)</li>
<li>preparation for examinations (e.g. crash course, mocked exam exercises,  mocked presentation and feedback)</li>
</ol>
<p>
Any jobs that are not covered in the above list but requested by the student can be consulted with the UFOffer staff to productize and commoditize.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<h3>三. 服务时间</h3>
<h3>Services Timeline</h3>
<div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>
对于基本的个人陈述修改服务，当学生向导师发起预约申请时，UFOffer工作人员会于24小时内联系到您（通过邮件，短信，及电话）。如果您时间安排较满或因其他原因不能接受预约，请于24小时内回复UFOffer工作人员。
</p>
<p>
Regarding the Standard Services on personal statement, as soon as the student books an application request to a chosen consultant, UFOffer staff will contact the corresponding consultant within 24 hours (via email, SMS or Telephone). Please duly reply to UFOffer staff within the next 24 hours, whether the consultant is available and accepts the appointment, or pre-occupied and hence unavailable under any circumstances.
</p>
</div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>
如果您接受学生的预约申请，请在UFOffer网站的My Appointment页面选择接受，并于5个工作日内完成个人陈述润色与修改工作。
</p>
<p>
If the consultant accepts the request, please confirm on the UFOffer website under the page of “My Appointment” by choosing “Accept Assignment”, and complete the standard services within 5 working days.
</p>
</div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>对于拓展服务，具体服务时间与规则请与UFOffer工作人员协商。</p>
<p>Regarding the Premium Services, please contact UFOffer staff upon request to agree the timeline and sign-off criteria.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h3>四. 质量要求</h3>
<h3>Quality Control</h3>
<div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>对于基本的个人陈述修改服务，UFOffer配备了专业的质量控制团队，团队中每个成员都是就职于高校或者曾就职于高校的资深教育行业人士。UFOffer致力于高端名校申请与完美的用户体验，每封经过导师修改的文书必须经过UFOffer质量控制团队的审核后，导师才能够获得相应的报酬。</p>
<p>Regarding the Standard Services, UFOffer has employed professional quality control team which consists of seasoned practitioners in the higher education industry. UFOffer has dedicated to high end user experience for the top university applicants and students. Every application document and course assignment must be checked and signed-off by the QA team before the consultant receives their monetary rewards.</p>
</div>
<div class="one-piece">
<p>对于拓展服务，UFOffer团队为学生配备了私人学习助理。当学生出现对于课程或相关服务不满意时，UFOffer的私人学习助理会介入协调并调查原因。</p>
<p>Regarding the Premium Services, UFOffer has prepared students with dedicated client manager, whenever the student raises issues about the services, UFOffer client manager will conduct proper investigation and reach a fair conclusion for both parties.</p>
</div>
